The "Easy" Chords (for Beginners...)
-------------------------------------
By Andreas Itten (aitten@access.ch)
Commedts, Suggestions.... are welcome


Hello there, I decided to show very Easy Chords. This will include 
some Major and Minor Chords.The Chords use as many strings as possible and because
of that they sound very Large and especially good with one Guitar.
They are not useful if there's a Keyboard, Piano... around. These Chords are
good for strumming. (especially on Acoustic Guitar). 

Have fun ! (Simplicity Rules !)

